<h3><a name="what-is-kalatheme"></a>What flavor is Kalatheme?</h3>
<h3>
<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;">Kalatheme is a very convenient theme to use, and should be the default theme for Panopoly, with all due respect. Peruse its&nbsp;<a href="https://drupal.org/project/kalatheme" target="_blank">Drupal project page</a>. &nbsp;Panopoly + Bootstrap 3 + Bootstrap themes + browser based sub-theme generator (&lt;-&nbsp;<a href="http://bootswatch.com/" target="_blank">Bootswatch</a>, etc., etc.!) + views grids + reusable custom CSS classes that can be registered as optional in any panels pane + advanced stuff for the folks that, inline with Kalatheme philosophy, don't like to admit they use it:<a href="https://drupal.org/node/2167227" target="_blank">Sass and Compass Tools</a>.</p>
